data.description: Discover this gem built by Knight Homes with over $75,000 in upgrades, every detail meticulously considered. The porch boasts double wood doors with 3/4 glass, setting the tone for what lies beyond. The 2-story foyer entrance sets the stage for your homeCOs elegance that awaits.  Enjoy formal dining in the exquisite dining room or enter the family room, featuring a fireplace that invites relaxation and it flows seamlessly into the oversized breakfast area.  Delight in the gourmet-style kitchen, complete with a spacious island and abundant storage. The kitchen is a chef's dream, showcasing a painted cabinet vent hood and cabinets special ordered for the home chef.  The exceptional Owner's Suite located on the main level, has bay windows and boasts a breathtaking stand alone tub, with a surprise window decoration and a large walk-in closet.  Upstairs, discover four additional large bedrooms, along with a full Jack and Jill bath and another full bath. The open family area upstairs, is perfect for gatherings and entertainment.  Leading out from the double kitchen doors is a Gameday Porch with fireplace, extending the entire kitchen/breakfast area perfect for the grill and summer nights of entertaining. Notice an additional attached garage with a convenient entry door from the driveway, and an additional half bath with a mudroom featuring a built-in bench. Every detail has been meticulously considered, from the color of the grout in the baths to the delightfully placed trim throughout the home to the additional lighting throughout to added insulation to an additional showerhead in the master. See the attached list of upgrades in the documents.
